 start, and we love showing the difference that professional cleaning can make.\nStay with us until the end to see the full before-and-after reveal\u2014you won\u2019t believe the results! \ud83c\udfe1\u2728\nFollow us for more amazing transformations, cleaning tips, and satisfying before & after videos.", "hashtags": [], "mentions": [], "url": "https://www.instagram.com/p/Da1MmVtRlD1/", "commentsCount": 0, "dimensionsHeight": 1920, "dimensionsWidth": 1080, "displayUrl": "https://instagram.ffxe1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t51.82787-15/747613004_18081825926659846_3132637724864537506_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&_nc_ht=instagram.ffxe1-1.fna.fbcdn.net&_nc_cat=110&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gGGRe4qD6O0EGRRpZHV1imDWES8aDaaKeY-SS_CT8pWeiNzx6vXK1zhCnR_dqjvrIg&_nc_ohc=fBDW-bW_GDEQ7kNvwE-ClFe&_nc_gid=2vhXVC3vqQNG5Mb9_Bqdpg&edm=APU89FABAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_AQCc8GP0uKe-bLi7mVStgYWGeOixkLD_wEpv3gA18JUiFQ&oe=6A61D633&_nc_sid=bc0c2c", "images": [], "videoUrl": "https://instagram.ffxe1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/o1/v/t2/f2/m86/AQN9CkwGweYoKbtabMbhQ42Uo01jo6kmclTTV1mSp_0s4q0m22LC5R1KqHw3itwalxmBfp2KkJkFXrwTFQybpvU4T9eM80VR9HidJLE.mp4?_nc_cat=100&_nc_oc=AdodE2DfzPn64wzpAQHIPiL7u7jMNUFp58Er8W3Cqvdcu5jl3Eu7555gVNv5W9mpss4&_nc_sid=5e9851&_nc_ht=instagram.ffxe1-1.fna.fbcdn.net&_nc_ohc=KuqVkGypZ0gQ7kNvwHpyN8T&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6Inhwdl9wcm9ncmVzc2l2ZS5JTlNUQUdSQU0uQ0xJUFMuQzMuNzIwLmRhc2hfYmFzZWxpbmVfMV92MSIsInhwdl9hc3NldF9pZCI6MjExMjgzNDA5MDExNjk3MCwiYXNzZXRfYWdlX2RheXMiOjIsInZpX3VzZWNhc2VfaWQiOjEyMzc0LCJkdXJhdGlvbl9zIjo1MCwidXJsZ2VuX3NvdXJjZSI6Ind3dyJ9&ccb=17-1&vs=7febb0aecaf6358e&_nc_&_nc_gid=2vhXVC3vqQNG5Mb9_Bqdpg&_nc_ss=7a22e&_nc_map=urlgen_bucketless&_nc_zt=28&oh=00_AQCqMAPJ6rjz-KNhx8o9iNbOKBH8L3UafvRs8kL3fVkfCw&oe=6A5DF075", "likesCount": 6, "videoViewCount": null, "timestamp": "2026-07-15T23:03:03.000Z", "childPosts": [], "ownerUsername": "allenettoyage", "ownerId": "49845611845", "productType": "clips", "isCommentsDisabled": false}, {"id": "3941537404291447942", "type": "Video", "shortCode": "DazJ2LTtPyG", "caption": "This client gave us a $300 tip. \u2764\ufe0f\n\nWhen she first called us, she said, \u201cI\u2019m so sorry. My house is in very bad condition.\u201d\n\nI told her, \u201cPlease don\u2019t worry. We\u2019re not here to judge you. We\u2019re here to help.\u201d\n\nWhen we arrived, we saw that the house needed a lot of work. One member of our team spent 7 hours cleaning just one bathroom. She was very tired, but she wanted to leave it perfectly clean.\n\nThe kitchen, the oven, and every corner of the house needed a deep cleaning.\n\nLittle by little, everything became clean again.\n\nWhen we finished, the client started crying.\n\nShe cried when she saw the bathroom.\nShe cried when she saw the kitchen.\nShe cried when she saw the oven.\n\nShe hugged us and said she was so happy.\n\nShe told us she never wanted her home to get like that again and that she would keep calling us to help take care of it.\n\nBefore we left, she gave us a $300tip.\n\nFor us, it wasn\u2019t about the money.\n\nIt was about making someone happy again and knowing that our work made a real difference.\n\nSometimes, cleaning a home is about much more than cleaning. Sometimes, it\u2019s about giving someone a fresh start.\n\n\u2764\ufe0f Thank you for trusting us.\n\nFollow us for more cleaning transformations and real stories from Canada.", "hashtags": [], "mentions": [], "url": "https://www.instagram.com/p/DazJ2LTtPyG/", "commentsCount": 0, "dimensionsHeight": 1920, "dimensionsWidth": 1080, "displayUrl": "https://instagram.ffxe1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t51.82787-15/748070786_18081701399659846_7837811904398158120_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&_nc_ht=instagram.ffxe1-1.fna.fbcdn.net&_nc_cat=110&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gGGRe4qD6O0EGRRpZHV1imDWES8aDaaKeY-SS_CT8pWeiNzx6vXK1zhCnR_dqjvrIg&_nc_ohc=_IAWznp1bMkQ7kNvwHBHk3a&_nc_gid=2vhXVC3vqQNG5Mb9_Bqdpg&edm=APU89FABAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_AQAoScuzoJ21RDEMwW30YrgEnjo0iKC834AD5sFXdYJlJw&oe=6A61E064&_nc_sid=bc0c2c", "images": [], "videoUrl": "h